<footer id="kontak" class="bg-[#1B2230] text-[#C9CDD6] py-16">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-10 mb-12">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="bg-[#F2711C] text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">miro</span>
          <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">Mie Yamin & Ayam</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-sm">
          Kedai mie yamin & mie ayam dengan resep turun-temurun. 
          Fresh setiap hari, porsi melimpah, harga bersahabat.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 bg-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[#F2711C] transition-colors" aria-label="Instagram">
